          "component_id": "customize",
          "data": {
            "data": {
              "parsed_content": [
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 10,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Keqing_icon.png",
                      "menu_id": 2,
                      "name": "刻晴",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "刻晴突破會增加暴擊傷害，剛好與該武器的副詞綴互補；且刻晴自身基礎生命值較高，剛好符合武器的優點，可以說是非物理流派刻晴的畢業武器。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 27,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Jean_icon.png",
                      "menu_id": 2,
                      "name": "琴",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "琴的基礎生命值是單手劍角色中最高的，非常符合該武器的優點；武器副詞綴是",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:#ffe14b"
                      ],
                      "text": "暴擊率",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "，很適合隊伍中作為副C兼治療的琴。不過，這把武器不適合在隊伍中純作為治療角色的琴。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 32,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Kamisato Ayaka_icon.png",
                      "menu_id": 2,
                      "name": "神里綾華",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "雖然該武器對佩戴冰套四件套的神里綾華來說，很容易有",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:#ffe14b"
                      ],
                      "text": "暴擊率",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "溢出的情況，但對佩戴充能四件套的神里綾華來說是用來打融化的首選武器。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "alignment": "center",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "amount": 1,
                      "display_style": "card",
                      "ep_id": 31,
                      "icon_url": "https://bbs.hoyolab.com/hoyowiki/picture/character/Kamisato Ayato_icon.png",
                      "menu_id": 2,
                      "name": "神里綾人",
                      "type": "custom_entry"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                },
                {
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "神里綾人突破會增加暴擊傷害，與磐岩結綠副屬性的高",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "bold",
                        "color:#ffe14b"
                      ],
                      "text": "暴擊率",
                      "type": "text"
                    },
                    {
                      "styles": [
                        "color:#ffffff"
                      ],
                      "text": "互相配合，可以打出優秀的暴擊；且神里綾人元素戰技下的浪閃傷害具有生命值加成，因此此武器非常適合神里綾人。",
                      "type": "text"
                    }
                  ],
                  "type": "paragraph"
                }
              ]
            }
          }
        }
      ]
